ing: 12 ounces spaghetti squash, peeled, seeded, and cut into 3-inch pieces
n: Slow Cooker Spaghetti Squash Chicken Soup
des: "This slow cooker recipe mixes chicken, spaghetti squash, diced tomatoes, and bell pepper for an easy soup preparation."
ins:
Stir spaghetti squash, tomatoes, chicken broth, chicken, bell pepper, salt, sugar, parsley, basil, oregano, garlic powder, and onion powder together in a slow cooker.
Cook on Low for 5 to 6 hours.
